</font></font></b>"<font face="Verdana"><font size="-1">In
1999 Darian Sahanaja of the Wondermints commisioned instrument designer
Tom Polk to build an updated version of the Electro-Theremin (renamed the
Tannerin) for an upcoming tour with Brian Wilson....</font></font></font>
</p><center><b><i><font face="Verdana"><font color="#000066"><font size="-1">--February
2001 issue of Electronic Musician</font></font></font></i></b></center>
